OL,7,FVisitors to the BBC Genome/BBC
OL,8,FProgramme Index in recent months have
OL,9,Fbeen becoming increasingly frustrated
OL,10,Fwith technical issues preventing
OL,11,Faccess.
OL,13,F"502 Bad Gateway" errors were a
OL,14,Ffrequent sight. Unusually long waits
OL,15,Ffor requested content to finally appear
OL,16,Fwas also a fairly common experience.
