OL,6,
OL,7,FIt's not clear why these experiences
OL,8,Fwere unique to this particular portion
OL,9,Fof the BBC's website but it certainly
OL,10,Fsuggests the content is hosted on less
OL,11,Frobust infrastructure than the rest of
OL,12,Fthe corporation's online offerings.
OL,14,FHowever, in the last week or so, a new
OL,15,Fmeasure has been put in place `
OL,16,Fpresumably to better control the load
OL,17,Fon whatever hosting arrangement is in
OL,18,Fplace for the Programme Index content.
