OL,6,
OL,7,FVisitors to BBC Genome/Programme Index
OL,8,Fmust now participate in a short test,
OL,9,Fto prove they are human.
OL,11,FThis quick visual test should keep out
OL,12,Fmany bots and crawlers, and reduce
OL,13,Fstrain on the hosting server(s), and
OL,14,Fprovide a better quality experience for
OL,15,Flegitimate users.
OL,17,FIt certainly seems to be working so
OL,18,Ffar.
